                <div class="card-body">
                  <h5 class="card-title">ICTAK Paatshala</h5>
                  <p class="card-text">ICT Academy of Kerala is a Social Enterprise created in a Public Private Partnership model (PPP) for imparting ICT skills to the youths of Kerala.</p>
