                  <p class="card-text">A Kerala Development and Innovation Strategic Council (K-DISC) initiative, Kerala Knowledge Economy Mission (KKEM)</p>
                  <a href="https://knowledgemission.kerala.gov.in/" class="btn btn-primary">Go To DWMS</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div> -->

